My vim configuration backup

Install:
sudo apt-get install vim
cp vimrc /home/$USER/.vimrc
mkdir /home/$USER/.vim
cp -r vim/* /home/$USER/.vim/

Install Plugins:
Launch vim and run :PluginInstall
To install from command line: vim +PluginInstall +qall

